metadata.name: HOZUKI #1
metadata.description: A secret research station explodes, the sky suddenly darkens, and many people have disappeared. When they wake up they find themselves in a virtual reality world called Hozuki.  Only the strong can survive in this world, become a hero or die. The journey begins, there are many factions and weapons for players to become stronger. It's not just a game, it's a whole new world where justice is done and lots of challenges ahead. Becoming a Hero in Hozuki, will you?
